                <strong>CAGR:</strong> +25.8% annually for 11 years</p>

                <div class="warning-box">
                    <h3>Reality Check</h3>
                    <p>These returns look incredible—and they are. But notice the Max Drawdowns: -66% for Nvidia, -73% for Tesla, -76% for Meta. Could you have held through a 70% drop? Most people panic-sell at the bottom. The calculator shows the "if you held" scenario. Real returns depend on your psychology.</p>
